profile.description: Hello, my name is Felipe, I am 18 years old and I am a passionate student of systems engineering. My cheerful and creative personality drives me to approach programming challenges with enthusiasm. Additionally, my ability to lead and collaborate as a team helps me achieve solid results. I am always excited to learn and grow in this ever-evolving field.

Although my work experience is limited, I am eager to apply my knowledge in innovative ways
